erg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uHnI5pJGV0zzAMiwpjJH59vRj8rylng9yoGc7HVj6CrszR618vX0Zuz7nkrRywlqGg386ju3GO5IaD2HCScj4y3vw46POracNfIQGPEE3F0waNLtGEwgrqyeV97Qt8fyhMvwu5GIzH5liQkj8fmObXp0a53KSSgO-qymqU6d3XC-fjm08EK61E1UpZ2SSJOAqQb9I6nRAFOdTsScFVn5qIQNsDKG6Da3ewYr6tU1lIT3vD816IVYZYdooMdW0lPwCVGxA7JFD9GltbiXHIVug2lv-gnFfQO3Odye0nxgFajwJPuLRjsh-MF9wZl2WauMjg%3D%3D" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1099799&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li=12375017&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=01212025" style="width: 108px !important; display: block;" width="108" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美国近一半州的总检察长&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uODQMSvN87pG_8_G6mI_YwlC8wIa-WXBZFbemLa_YlBY5edCsPHG8MSg2W76HA9JBDvYm3hXMDHmXKA3WcgCu7a8eUvn6elXd4qXh0bhP6q3fjJHQ6vO1X0UUOKTaWxnx6PcsqNSs8ugXnHXDKl1zJ8yLdnjOWA-iFAw8T13h3XTMPZa4g_4tDQLtx9M17IpAgY_EA0M9aPEU6ElvTb54lZBOQKVMIm0Wrhmbu3aAZzLtfGnYbqZG4j-_Wv75tQSNxLIYyu8UG95HO_B-opoa-A0TPVIG1txGotDfksPKkIQCQglYO8lUMP77ZzqZ1sBeA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;起诉唐纳德·特朗普总统，&lt;/a&gt;要求其终止与生俱来的公民身份的行政命令。法律学者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uLXH3zZ8hdiljHPctIDuYNwyb93wm7-HjGH26LIze4SqPN6oUHR0sLL1mjYKKGlwf95LeE_GRoVLQxQ8JqYK7-wWQnHqBHdecJL4KSHucYRNq0CVra5Ba6c8Wt0SNJbrptMnICGQGC3WJEfBNEPIibTYcMQqafhoAkmITWP2SApIhd0zDI8CHJI3WbyBbtMzLbcbSHkWT1HdTudd0itVp1H7X12IkZ10psipkm-kquYKO8IhqjCJo1jH1GzE0Ee4rcm3urtjY9SJLvbKitmxwqIC7tGAwzgbKGNI2Dctk4EBILBywUv2dvPQ7khGCnnf5bFyGUf4jePj0cZ3mMKh9qN3D3N2M-TDRqgDcEQLsNgswCGbZBaGjWVMeTHKGGRifhzAE1DlN-8ZthGpEwyVYKfawwwYwzg7mYyE5MiJCHxlUZdc5xyBJUhZ13xKsGAlJIhw9Y4piycQmgHOUvI_rZTS_ItMZiktaIo0-D3U5c04XFeBjTDx8K83cunRLNW3k9L6z_MwMvua7V--g6jXHAkGgKej9NL2VosG_14DgpGb6u5HUv1ptvl5ufXB_bzrCA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;普遍认为&lt;/a&gt;，这一移民政策&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uG7gd2ueqQ0LBjTbHVsWkpCap7czUI51wALYb7YZYJ1bi54Kp8P4fBabiK4ZumESOfjdj0y0Q5oRp0o3fDEbYI-DxrKJoKHjpa_3OuLJ5BV-tpnG249CE-wpfSWahRI1baft2tZghoGt1A3ITSAH7QruLVz0wubF1MlmenKPFoOwLP0hhpDQce7PJVAZT4H3sMIt_xfNB0tT1mph9t_9SfVyeUHZ876gn-ROtTV0mWyaXWOi8EUabLS9ykP7ZVdLrAfP-w8eLd2sKsvlZMcaManOR2uoUYNGlRPzrX-jU5LhQztcq7ZwDdd9i2WEzlw7Oizo2q3ONXV-3lE11V7itgxIEC50TSp6af1KpAiCX5NC5bzMuQtZjaV2Ez-Kj4HMhnMey77QmnAkvgciDENZ47z7qbQ4yqZQJ_j-ULW81mr0DO9WAIrUuDZUrKpr1lnzYGK_A3z0wpN2R1_KdrLtMUB696_85lidzI6YAhUoh38LNqJOvpi4gf6rDHUb9pW0ef4vLWs1HVQTie7vnvIp7ktJi5RLq2oaP-5J6m79Cpku" target="_blank"&gt;已载入美国宪法&lt;/a&gt;，保证美国出生的儿童无论其父母的身份如何，都是公民。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;这项行政命令是共和党周一重返白宫后不久发布的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uAgQdQMndo1mBqUJ6PK0yY_elzgobjSVbg0Q41l6wEScNoO0H0xM_r7DxEDpw9-1On3C-mmUU45SjxeIi9J8Ded82OFEY9iUCPcmhBVN93vncz9U8ljoUDo-FeJOy0ivlD5cp1CGNCQuDGM7eLtK94Pb8nH_5Bm-an0Mc0OGzd061OpyKJ8oHlYb0y8jTxhwP4vKqSyR0LX4cYbyJa2c0X2_8EGc5IL5bGfVsqCCgAHv8cJAldBvchckaSxoSO6WwHuRVpUK_GUgl0uMBnGnoLtp3vwgrT24p1-UgIDbJwG9M4knxE1yeAAC5_aU7JInZA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;一系列行政命令之一&lt;/a&gt;，旨在颠覆一个多世纪的法律先例。如果法院维持该命令，该命令也将适用于合法在美国的人，但只是暂时的，例如游客、学生和持有工作签证的人。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;大约 18 名民主党总检察长在马萨诸塞州的联邦法院起诉特朗普，而另一个由四个州组成的联盟在西雅图提起了类似的诉讼，这标志着针对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uMONl5_Aaoib8OkZNBCXYcVRJ2zF9TLB39Y65ovz_2zGEtPSQPQvuD0iDXQh1lAASyJJMlmkpt4Zk3jQZjD5xZ2NHU7dLakKmAnEq7tgXEndQT4j6RXwwFe6F9_uVdtIEh-Gk-shE4SEAiQ8XB9rHHIKwtc8a7yB_LjuMk_3jtGNnEkNksWXfFbbyk9oFvm-DWMtBjI9BWdHxTmZ9yIWGcplQ4RAPLue0DcdvNuW43Rozk8eguNX1ryilpaj1jzZlAWkFEs61ay1sB9qI4ANlUdRQ9n1erykPjYybJf2jumkwomzqgfwxhLdJKhCTVXWdQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;特朗普移民政策的&lt;/a&gt;一场漫长的法律斗争迈出了第一步，这场法律斗争可能会在美国结束最高法院。长期以来，出生公民权一直被认为受到宪法&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uF0IIe1GAbpJcBxC8rFnujtn1Orqk7m0gpV93L6qmsbDAsDW5HwNe_LAyqb3Rjctnl55_zTfg85AcfCIP1IlT5y-dflypw7eB09AcYXcymv2gWVXsCZ8VCSBPgFfguUwlNGiOe_ioZB3CIum2r7_Qhxornqz5zNBQEMNdDDhHhuvwos3qlSNHbMl7IJWvbbzc2Q9kIY111rzskM9wlMrN6aBRPAvssC50C34PlBIMkUiC1P3FkgP9huI8IaF_zSwf3NB5pdhj2IrzYc6tZZE_eOyytUOSTTWgEX9KstEi7tenfRBkHDEYgYM8VdagVo7LWFYwbAXvtqYE4md42xJ_8Wrn3mYqOMrkb8bhDkhfwATENba2D3R0srKfnn3U7Sh3cH3JSLniBjlnHNA1qAwQ98%3D" target="_blank"&gt;第十四修正案&lt;/a&gt;的保障，该修正案规定“所有在美国出生或入籍并受其管辖的人都是美国公民”。 &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;— &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uNj-j1s5wor3znvkFevw2nOf67SootgMRnlevkMR3PLIJ1JFzzfS-GeTrjkXTcQLKLSHak5M7f3qHj4TH1GXo4Guy6Hyi8xyz4NM4aDFaGXCv3zNmwEnOsiM9jhq1qWP3ruP8Y_f0pgCjzDJRjao6nX5JQmo0dW1h7Ylf2wM-TXGcLvodM7b_Es60VwxIdE4K89Vzq4Do9deIZOBv08Jiti7p_JEHvxMGIhL7GoN4KhSRnJAiwq3vbxao4RrDMIjEpAYNbsk_O2eYbZUTpYqlIOixa6j2E8XP-KRL4zm9M5Zt-IwpSzHPQpXxD4DwOQEQQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;乔丹·帕克·厄布&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;与此同时，特朗普与软银、OpenAI 和甲骨文的首席执行官一起&lt;/strong&gt;宣布了一项新的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uNcXFs6wPFkvWyu3p8OeV8ijN-TOT-HuZ9lKIePrSPrRAVlLAhSVs_fsqMzf1oqR0qAwmHa_wqKS_CQmJmbkeyyVZn7z09FDn4dYorMR4kvOQFP8Rm3CrVrLY4DSSqBnpnnXKm9wiwCG5GdDAcJKvVSXdy_RQZyXXyiD9WDgY1qWVKNIDdmVhZkdNehUsLqvU1VRkmsJMQ3zR2iWcUo8Ns4w3iPw9pKCu06Ua0P-aGUenSQX_oe3AbVSuVL3pbsdH5W4isDi7MXdDIJi28BHK_GuXIqAQC4XLANBe7WqREpBUOEOuxmgj13Kp43FYfigow%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;人工智能投资计划&lt;/a&gt;。周二下午，软银的孙正义、OpenAI 的萨姆·奥尔特曼和甲骨文的拉里·埃里森与特朗普一起公布了对人工智能基础设施的 1000 亿美元初始投资，未来四年可能扩大到 5000 亿美元。一天前，特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uPZLBfRD1Xwmmqo22DDko6bLEArQbufwoJtcoLvfj2qmjOUo9N3ehaZeOzXi5ap4pCuFy3jRpnNS94j5Ebq8QjkpG_8GNnn6knLALfkfgkUjgkBXdPqiJABT9ENrH30NvW0q4bm6WZUDNl6OL_3_xVBtnNtTkLrXlUpfOqnPx2oaWPToElee_MB10u1eDObcwVSrz0f1JTyxGiHcjbfaTuBk1213r6jry0w8SkesrFTTPSru5H8Yz7Ifhv_3I_bC7CVtp_Lx-Gdldxb43Tibq92eMnZuPprLNfeaLvN93-ZROr7jKsGbahj7_KarYQr7gg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;撤销了&lt;/a&gt;前总统乔·拜登关于人工智能的全面行政命令，立即停止对人工智能开发人员实施关键的安全和透明度要求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uNcXFs6wPFkvWyu3p8OeV8i1sQ9PKuI5x7a04QnJkCIlhPJ2ShHCmSFSGmdSBrEpWUlNN63NvIf25CzgkGJONOuuxdsk5y3KZnKsS_C6iyNtYoLsJAU_kYg8-sP6QInJghHx3AZ70PnxHLJy65JcoDwoi0Fg6BokYNwTOUjHFuvo5VF3wg3Fpt44a_X1rT_bjoF2kYuq2LnTugDkKXgl8a3I26F1n43hDAOR2ie6uplz-L7P8yCKWSF8gJouEQNEyv38BClnptNhrBz-KtzhZZi9XQ-1B2PUuJV124BRE0jCKCj4xMoPerlQkY3q6JgjEQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3K85Btsymb0/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3K85Btsymb0/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;周二，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（左）在白宫罗斯福厅与软银首席执行官孙正义、甲骨文首席技术官拉里·埃里森和 OpenAI 首席执行官萨姆·奥尔特曼发表讲话。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：安德鲁·哈尼克/盖蒂图片社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;高盛宣布进行重大改革。&lt;/strong&gt;该银行刚刚报告&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uITEKtY_0GcFAhjZeFO97snO-quCkeHe3hazH-jo3GHr61R1ViK6XETu2_VF19FyNM5JfO6tRkQYLZAUgcCIcUBMpH4-pMJvYTHHvHaAww22_Md2ZVZEPZH-tiHfOqjVjrAgcK-9Tn7BQQNwDqUUbLMoTP4dUnybMbFhuXioplAhE5N3gSlS60gI_IB0vcAv81ITNBc9YFNTPXjS6wC4xwei69Q6xkN3JOA6lh6BD-AmuEhNArDUqucZdn1E2qCWYOunv0v8I97knzskreBWY1TnL_rYJ_a5xCbde4wWAjC8Kc7a3CU6BuieovVjMcC5FA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;利润激增&lt;/a&gt;，迎来了下一代领导层，为其股票、固定收益和银行部门&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uBMh9El1YcOd6Xgy7QGj9EkXTjtekcOuj23VdTww35MyxZalCfhdO58LxZJADgNPm2moRCgNwD3hNXtuqSRMENPDBka-zQ75QMb52lRV--kmqW3lN4U7OTD0jSS07yPeBN9HibIPMerivDMhNA09MioBE1Q44vMH056BqeaJvpH1EbKaLMWTpRCgzAkn6qEaDpN3PlgO_RNp-TOigJN0aGD4qGgalWTDWx9fqPb9bDAVoo7xDk_Pwt5daNYDdbZrBtMYFVNmkxNprXgMn67wcIG8ECzDXdJexFYu_V15x7v2ude1uNVx5tfBQdptAtRDyw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;聘请了新的全球领导者&lt;/a&gt;。 Erdit Hoxha、Cyril Goddeeris 和 Dmitri Potishko 将负责股票业务； Kunal Shah、Anshul Sehgal 和 Jason Brauth 将负责固定收益业务； Kim Posnett、Matt McClure 和 Anthony Gutman 将领导银行业。这些变化是近年来高盛除首席执行官大卫·所罗门核心团队之外的未来领导力最重大的提升。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;由于去年其两只主要对冲基金的表现低于同行，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;布雷文·霍华德 (Brevan Howard) 削减了约 7% 的交易人员&lt;/strong&gt;。据称，此次终止&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uLzAOaPTbOfncwn86wGfYzVk2_RF8-DEngpiDaxVmi731No43_LTObKLWZ2MwEL9tAzKWJKBM-n98g2alGM_ZoByGBuz5nIc2S-pveBDrBxAx28HEaistCWAtXk8qQf2Prahw-6OHYgVlpHC0s3no2eY0g6thD-KYJNh838Acr9QwN2Oo7_NmuWD9McR8nD6WsFkF_C8u4nFDTf1APzAZLB6P5v_wvS6iHZxv9pZ52ZBMxx5ZhlGg9TEsSAWzZtU-tHcxRMDq9alzB5U2fR7FpJKxqPooYcuMXFQRHd2_KF89IoJZXE4kgIKKsPX-YSkuQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;影响了 Brevan Howard 纽约、伦敦和阿布扎比全球办事处的约 12 名交易员&lt;/a&gt;，目前只剩下约 150 名交易员。继去年进行类似削减之后，这家宏观贸易公司在每年两次的审查中淘汰了当前一批交易员。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=52eb0d1b7e5f4a36809afd4de0392d2f&amp;amp;_e=C1ja8aSXX561BMl9m9P6uFLMq_uGFpzqU6G7LCChV7RB8DD-SEpBkjfrSpNpW7OB9WyFv7XXmejJ7GEs-BL_rl3NiMx2FjmlzQTXiWKPsrTJBeoBPqyMeg7b08egaENOWPezRNVlC7Dw-Wj0hTou4rknDrpl0XcSXMk-qqjnnGxh1kaPJjUEvk-KAZSMg2O270AgLKQHKbfy_CYEn6dkxrhdPjVzH_XWfnJPxlPnn9tVSzCGplf6xoGQgmf-ArOFQDx79mNTh0E5QOxfHXOs2ffalaDW0P8PThLn-1o0VZn5VVLPFBUUYp1naf1EO5oHwKOGhxX1Oa13Sd2tzBvtlA%3D%3D" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQS00V4.EmgQ/v0/550x381.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img class="email-ssl-image" src=