o4fBbdGp5uJZs0hfsjbTK" target="_blank"&gt;彭博之家&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj9_oXeMgwH1JJ0_KslruVDCWQqUn0K_g0pvp5IJC-U1IQ0wRJyRfbAjeh0FzY3wai-N2hqt47jNZX09jxMf2sghckeCoPbjXE7h7QGRF4QQHAOaSC1XmxLyIdUuDJq5U_dFwGWat9Tq86s3ovWjiBuPrVP_KlhW4dC37jQLFomAl0LfEmAVtGzjU6MmmVO5sTBjiOL7KbFjnnIcBjW605P_OXnNenEOxz0INCk2cedxbclGISmVsPReyKtLttcNqDwLxC3PJCxCAv4h2yq14TM62qrE6ybIlx2DR4jiRxiXq" target="_blank"&gt;在这里注册&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idhGjE8ERWoU/v0/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idhGjE8ERWoU/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;聚会时间&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在达沃斯会议室工作的财务主管们都以不同程度的兴奋迎接唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;掌舵美国经济的一位以市场为中心的资深交易撮合者带来了一个充满机遇的新时代——可以赚钱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;摩根大通欧洲、中东和非洲地区首席执行官兼全球银行业务联席主管 Filippo Gori 表示：“客户有一定&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj5_QonIYZp862WE04Gw7iGvZjnwWlO1jXSz_XqQdCNsJairHRkwyBWhwSsP0Griiqk5aGTJCimKVWHn8-cDUZQTHT_PUFU-bieRwuOgeq2B3dvOfjwknYj0j9zMkwbF_nc3MQG1sq7_z9S4OwfLskQhlWGjWAf_Ux_HwfrIxV2mtzGINN81RT9db1lyboJ2X8euRQ2JsXByTOdpHeNVyXW8%3D" target="_blank"&gt;程度的兴奋感&lt;/a&gt;。”他将这部分归因于“政府的亲商态度”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普上任后的第一个小时就已经就从边境安全到公民规则和贸易等各个方面发布了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj5PahWZYGbRHLseE1GtZ_lwp-lT4XAexODrqyn3Bqi13r9noTwXwtEd3ObvEvLbwhbxgfaQbvvX8qQdqDD861_baCg1iOPvXD8VTVr2eBJEovVuoM1-jmPwLhHyuWO0ZHQWZmKSP35mCfOVKf2Q_AnGeLymZFQ3lTJ1hjLfyFQQNzgwZoeyDe6T8iSSN7xPqmWh9Nn0FEmaL_bPAi6zAmd4%3D" target="_blank"&gt;一系列行政命令&lt;/a&gt;，美国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj1yZvxvmfR3Xc9dAho5-_SXlKi_Cv7hSvgjQcsX2ucJXv9dAWneP6xSS-sm9ZRZHIeEiiq5SLzeCxpkOzuobSVr1v6PK7r4_vUHFxW6QlT8CwJCMDq41qUCAMWZiYfnwx_oHPbGqzYIsZ3f5vj9AP7E_YRixg9qDWNL6sGp9B2XGOkToDMpAA9lXUcKewX-VDjXxrXw5y37_FIIXJRZ2XAw%3D" target="_blank"&gt;政权更迭&lt;/a&gt;的感觉是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj5PahWZYGbRHLseE1GtZ_lxlHkzh7YnX5xBbFAuIF20c4XsHlzaOAFe71QBeYoTxDDR0GJO6SX_3G6l9Zj_76ZYvXyhLk4DMIddClsgR4YraKIQyU5zEp8bEIwZgVEBahOs_xbJeSVT2KaxToLEUIAt1jK6aO_cqgIRQ27i5OWhltlRMmq1WfRyZpGaRei0xcDZA0pCIf2QOVPxWJ8hQ8bs%3D" target="_blank"&gt;显而易见的&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;摩根大通资产和财富管理部门负责人玛丽·埃尔多斯表示，戈里所在银行的工作人员在“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj7h5kqtaqH0POhPrgbyZGFET8_4L3s02pdY28Z-KeY4RRSGUT818GxEOWTYIgjAlQJcCkFesSV7rB1duF7cwvjwQFyp66fVl16gdrGpR7TCIYvnuoFVT08W9HUAfrHLAtBITPrKwHbu2KJs74nNXvBC2wVsaJ5frFNPOoxbURsblObeOLtVyw8C_bSzIIl2JIvyCDQg95-sW8w_bfdqoxDw%3D" target="_blank"&gt;作战室&lt;/a&gt;”彻夜不眠，以处理影响。她告诉专家小组，最初的迹象是“非常有利于商业环境”和经济处于“运行模式”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;富兰克林邓普顿投资公司首席执行官珍妮·约翰逊对此表示赞同，称市场将从中受益。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; “人们认为他将对经济有利，” &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj_h-vBmGoyWOa-bvekClxD77woDY38Fj3cvjSBBfWD9QQVpJ_vqpnP109-hy5ak_DI0iNaivrjdsw19L7dgOYv6wwNn3oegIdt5zWlDfYeFz28fOKge3YVB4TAnAGPD0fB0OF57CY91NgmNElrFHreJ2wDwgg0NWjSAzBLgOHt_RQnDRWgZdFyH3dmdeE61I6hKqP3Reg5JcH2Jv6DIt9CU%3D" target="_blank"&gt;她告诉彭博电视台&lt;/a&gt;。 “因此，这对公共和私人市场都有好处。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;她和同行们列举了特朗普计划中可能滋生动物精神的两个方面。一是支出和减税的前景，二是他热衷于取消规则，包括对银行的规则。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; “放松管制，尤其是明智的放松管制，将对许多企业有所帮助，”道富银行董事长兼首席执行官&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqjzKy6wzdgjFi1tBQfC_FfHQI4yCY1HKLL7yrtCL0313Ei4zlQnAbaATerJs_kJfPnyKM2Y_vL1Q_-gxuqN1dK_mqSiUbQmaBEyolQ5Sf8IggVpT5oxH3G1luUW0XveglB5mQg9MXVOfnTbggGEVuazZl3CsEjhOFGv5HH1t_yi7H5M1mi37MHib97O0_uqj-DCCmBoAO3IvgaEF0sCFObb8%3D" target="_blank"&gt;罗恩·奥汉利 (Ron O&amp;#39;Hanley) 表示&lt;/a&gt;。 “银行家和我们所有人的希望是，至少不会有更多的监管。” &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.AAIoJnTi6M/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.AAIoJnTi6M/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;一些欧洲银行家正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqjzEZsr7ZsF_230G5Y36IsQamlC0zvcw9SX0hE5wTt6dxRzgrsTZxZNZ8clLxFyt1c_jluzUjRNNXilF66Nypj7GEL7sLHV0-S5JykPY5NeeE6zXVRdaFECoBdeZ-Z-GX0EvoFZeTUtROrHPPpcYtF4TGRj40XqTXsIIdop_sVrxvB3m2-VjprAMdjM2Ged0aXoO0WR62mI1m1-qddqag7Z4%3D" target="_blank"&gt;羡慕地看着&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;联合信贷银行首席执行官安德里亚·奥塞尔表示：“预计美国在监管较少方面将远远领先于欧洲。” “这将使我们处于竞争劣势。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;并非达沃斯的每个人都具有金融业的派对精神。国际货币基金组织前&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj7vbM2D62Um373vWhkLopGSxdld24efMMdui0NhjP3TNKk3J7BI24CsHD2-0d_w_Qwy3VTHeI1UzYl12oxC9tPCXYRn9PWyYZaBkik7tvUk-mwJJdIM-DPZ-pBTBtgXbXVvkHCA-YZj6sFzLa3BQPoFla_IB8aCrKl8Y5bK_07OaHA-nP-ZigXi-mxXt301POGU6F4DcnZ8UhJjd3CJrOmY%3D" target="_blank"&gt;首席经济学家肯·罗格夫&lt;/a&gt;认为，与特朗普第一任期不同，他的许多政策&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj-5e5tAxaFMCtOzVWRv0cY98Iq3B65nTaIAMZP4-CDxf9BqivsQ1PnT26crl6rJxnMwIrEfLIloACo_YffueKSi7FdtV5yiMttfckfUT4rmSUHSB3tYZUFwc2EP66eLSEBYh39ZyRl49nNfNjFEKLCjXkg2StwUT9GncKe_7jjDnbwmwkae8g2sMcQ5-FOnPlsI8Ze6jncblg0beshZERoE%3D" target="_blank"&gt;无助于经济增长&lt;/a&gt;，更高的利率也无济于事。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; “他有很多第一次没有遇到的限制，” &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj-5e5tAxaFMCtOzVWRv0cY9Q8WJKdcYZ-qFlgvvvIH5rnzG0jG1KBAQnAZu_9zh3qDsQ5YWDOT3F1nMfyoG6LDL4AIAZSQhCuoV_KMkB4fS74_zuSwCVEMKljUwd4rD1PDg6cKpbwRCEJxHSEc4sCxlWrI5AIFnPH-L_G1YRCBzc6cN7S1KbEiaYMBDNs17NdzkgeD_0LxyDT_GF73oHIP4%3D" target="_blank"&gt;罗格夫说&lt;/a&gt;。 “我认为你无法期待我们上次的繁荣。” &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj8tjxMjTb5lidDe9o6zSkKm5vR4sr2Qn53r_ljRtMA03DgLDfuMGd3f26EYuiRebOgrzAje2pOq8vFet21CrSNbJeuEORZqLnyCiHqd0SOIrX7cRpV1-eUnLV2kScrsdSNKlzRriA2_nC7Vi8FmX0xRmo67T0FCpFfl3K7jbvEn8dNLaup_cEj0iJMAVoChafb-7b3P7FJpZNgydi2wJnp_jtfr7XKUURHASI0BrX336prvPG7q5pt5ABiBsB0eZZZOK2wgmn4pjBPtgJRW8eyyIiHSsU0Vosdo7uJUWIIEprzM82OC-NneToDLv8CSCmw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" border="0" class="lihide" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=868592&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=desktop&amp;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=12370734&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=01212025" style="display: block; height: auto; width: 100%;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" valign="top"&gt;&lt;!--[if !mso]&gt;&lt;!--&gt;&lt;div class="lishow" style="display: none; overflow: hidden; width: 0; line-height: 0;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj8tjxMjTb5lidDe9o6zSkKm5vR4sr2Qn53r_ljRtMA03DgLDfuMGd3f26EYuiRebOgrzAje2pOq8vFet21CrSNbJeuEORZqLnyCiHqd0SOIrX7cRpV1-eUnLV2kScrsdSNKlzRriA2_nC7Vi8FmX0xQV6yYWhd5QPwWQ4U3l2VRHD37sKqmtWQJq9YKfxz8UfHWH93h6m0dPK9bL-pBhVsGOBHQK3aFgVzMAjnwpr58sfRLQL5TH89zYvtsIakY1U6LU