jM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj3xMZUDrjojijUqYtM0Z_cbuRc6VOBh7EjWuwn2pmMGcZuJjWjEemoZadrMksp3jSoyPcOahUtRZD6CNK2K_QeEP4coli0IOEOMbnIAG24PR22SXy4q9BIvT2NkJOshy3HhkZLx9SUURvg5z-HrqO5Gr16whnziYHJDYl8lPPzOZYVH-BWOgqkFXN7OmJ241N7C5bN2C8TmshaI3qbkgqMU%3D" target="_blank"&gt;OpenAI Inc.&lt;/a&gt;首席财务官 Sarah Friar 将 Elon Musk 为阻止 ChatGPT 制造商成为营利性公司而提出的法律挑战描述为竞争策略。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;联合信贷银行的 Orcel 不会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj2wWuCpqlg2kO7lQGuVJCU0_cHtelvz62xCdu2H8wjq22OJzN7nsoAd7ARCkBrNGFmBrLchB-lWqy8WTWKjS0dDrSDfCU0wmkjdQ-u74bl4ISkpg-3npp92aGbj0kH4RN0X6i3xqKgSLP8aSfv9hn60QmmVVz_kSs7FFj2c2EKsz5svnpRRxdflY7tbhhN274CsmAynTsLFUBV56UxMX3qU%3D" target="_blank"&gt;不惜一切代价寻求收购德国商业银行&lt;/a&gt;，而瑞银集团的塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂正在考虑是否效仿华尔街同行&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqjy0cWHRigS0D1zQZRx_i_xLgZUznPVpw3VqtA0nd_QgxC2s-hb1FajZXbWY1WMPqiyhydyBac1FwyXdhcuoKu-2DORP3y2FRJ3mzULwsU-jCK81OcG6X8EBCHi6rZ08AqTrKu-rAgwmBnNhYu2cJMZVFWhnfyDuai9KQRfvovF2uUW0wrj6xhpdXdT0c3JLEAa5YcEulkJJuvPhl9NL3TJ4%3D" target="_blank"&gt;放弃一个重要的气候金融联盟&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;欧洲央行管理委员会成员 Francois Villeroy de Galhau 表示，央行有可能在即将举行的每次会议上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3d0a120d7fc&amp;amp;_e=wTejM_9rpeNumMEFkeTqj_5lTbSJIbGuM96yp4f2q8PzfsZlQH-fWe6bucZi1mnNJ2pUblC5boq0aSwpobtyUB5F55EEvU0LEnTR5lc8ylK2AS5Ktuy-UkjpM318AoDLslKq-7YbGyvlnl34AhjUrdAg-egyx1N6DFsbzvVw8Wbzy0T-ynIvjDBOGCfXOEU_aWGNnOvNWrQd45GoYMaUrPBonfpQnsXFUjHpSY5wciI%3D" target="_blank"&gt;降低利率&lt;/a&gt;，而他的德国同事 Joachim Nagel 则表示， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=42d17aa97b2b4a7cbf46c3