wajSB2TO31A0kG6fIM-uLl1EFJrjvdUW1bcC4T61F0ODAcGTQfGjqIU5TpT6_bdXVeGaFjCUY6_sAoSE1BZD"&gt;詹妮弗·A·德鲁希&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;人们普遍预期唐纳德·特朗普总统将下令&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=be63c1005c2c4a6890f66ef1ce035e8c&amp;amp;_e=mbZ-Iv2SEgh9k3FYOEs2zTKWM33jiaNX9P4-ERibhHQA_QPi8XqdCTreI8NzI1nUGFbU3N4Kfkbjso7lUZqN3iCOpZ3FAPH8krhQo3QqwU8d2O52GD8km3_xOHb6QVvl7tACCrU3fxrBKUaRoY67q-woxW8G3hEcwK6iQ0bwlYRebABGLHvRZPHugn8xTm5akK1sUlMKrMC6VV3TeRrrAl84hankjA9a1LX6bts3RM4hELRvoKRLiMYWx86UfNaS4-EoXFTeUUxrgUZby6IyPPHX8eSOh3oA25i1HuE68FZX8D3QvocFJptCSCju6OxFDRXu9hotVr62kztIAXQh-Px7o3blF9-a8pVjAHLK77mGfs3jGBz56x8MhishlXgf5ZAj15-Hm3kcPp0xP1N1zT45tL1Hi8qBx79UfSArRXNuQVmde_AnmSkYIO5e_rEHkUpAMwnqF3wKXzNXh9i0Q37f3hDrvKYaWD1sXY_ujNhX-NGKe_v_DgPkStBdDlQVXRHnwa1A8KacGOK9mmHGpZMSxpNyqBONg6HK1A4jGzaVYJNk2_4dLgpigzm6cEbCDDScwbZfkOBCQtorVBuzqvlUtVvY4KkD09HGVAiQ39kYr2TBGoWCXqzcoVG9HuCr63lmudYMCnJwt6lIoRmPiN9BNAZvE8hcgyOXcgQpnPv9kEh91heKKo6e0t9-9wQkyn-m8F2zXqjY8yhtV4BzHro0nT_t6QTCOiNdvTrdEYGI_RxLHnGV7wem5N9dJPcux_fAW4heZpMH66K30v-VZhx6-JkMr1YT0hN_N0rwKQuPeV24uQPcWY34uaQBQsC__iQ7AyJpeH8d6Ukpkm7jS73S3YBM4PVjJudEJpgTnrs%3D" target="_blank"&gt;退出《巴黎协定》&lt;/a&gt; ，但在他就职几小时后决定采取行动，突显了共和党承诺迅速改革美国能源和气候政策的严肃性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普在签署一封通知联合国美国打算退出该协议的信函之前表示：“我将立即退出不公平、片面的《巴黎气候协议》的剽窃行为。” “美国不会破坏我们自己的工业，而中国则肆意污染而不受惩罚。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;退出减排协议只是特朗普重返白宫第一天发起的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=be63c1005c2c4a6890f66ef1ce035e8c&amp;amp;_e=mbZ-Iv2SEgh9k3FYOEs2zTKWM33jiaNX9P4-ERibhHQA_QPi8XqdCTreI8NzI1nUGFbU3N4Kfkbjso7lUZqN3iCOpZ3FAPH8krhQo3QqwU8d2O52GD8km3_xOHb6QVvl7tACCrU3fxrBKUaRoY67q-woxW8G3hEcwK6iQ0bwlYRebABGLHvRZPHugn8xTm5akK1sUlMKrMC6VV3TeRrrAl84hankjA9a1LX6bts3RM4hELRvoKRLiMYWx86UfNaS4-EoXFTeUUxrgUZby6IyPPHX8eSOh3oA25i1HuE68FZX8D3QvocFJptCSCju6OxFBi0F6K9HwMSY0INMrPFbq8VwrvMWYor0ScPfoagyIe_pkj3xh7jmOYYAvJn50YuG2mtr0D02XOhFGZboHLszMzj7lSyaPZWwGvXAVExU_r-q6TkiVj90PdvR_UVJJZngVBhZsqwpW2iISHOl7ohLx1teO9ybQGnojZwSMe9DHb_7ExDJCnlI0R__gzPmO3E2aQRw4G79jna0R6HIkLbFKU2jpZLk9wmenp7vrxzvzWKat2g7h5cL83JRj6U9mCInUJnm_bbMdysPvZN9GtoX-EK_lQ703IGl2pAR-8TtNlxwJsi-D7LCnBffKWVTWc_GX9aQo1e9fDFj1O7ENxfABy7w0HufSyDZlOAZrImUfLMKeDe_uVhdCp-yEck6yOg9kBupe8GZL4p2aT2cyXr7DEp88tRttZHrYv_ZXso8x4jfjf6Ycaph6wMX-5Xys-Rw-RqOIo37osOeuD5I1o7CAOumyJVWHkwgjj46lVBDv81whwksdZlNhg7B4P9aEn8D80SWuyqZiwqzy4zRjmnwUc2Pi_6fLgbrcpoJ5nZ1caU%3D" target="_blank"&gt;众多变革&lt;/a&gt;之一，他将美国政策从应对气候变化转向促进化石燃料生产。特朗普在就职演说中发誓，他周一的行动“将结束绿色新政”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=be63c1005c2c4a6890f66ef1ce035e8c&amp;amp;_e=mbZ-Iv2SEgh9k3FYOEs2zTKWM33jiaNX9P4-ERibhHQA_QPi8XqdCTreI8NzI1nUGFbU3N4Kfkbjso7lUZqN3iCOpZ3FAPH8krhQo3QqwU8d2O52GD8km3_xOHb6QVvl7tACCrU3fxrBKUaRoY67q-woxW8G3hEcwK6iQ0bwlYRebABGLHvRZPHugn8xTm5akK1sUlMKrMC6VV3TeRrrAl84hankjA9a1LX6bts3RM4hELRvoKRLiMYWx86UfNaS4-EoXFTeUUxrgUZby6IyPPHX8eSOh3oA25i1HuE68FZX8D3QvocFJptCSCju6OxF925gM6A1Rzt3NSZ345vhoupI70D89NbmK2aw-6HwxYzCyaPvjR6uaHyBHkLqDVuXVX4-UBys0YEzZILmSfPaacaEhKHHmaL3WpOZvYp0g3khspanGE7zukda0vPSMqm3EhR_p2CwHZSJn_h01WIsyQ41e-FVUwMjcFLk-PvAyrBVF3RdnIMGfA6Hl22FISJIoTL_MQs10gNCX1V2mvKvg_CVFJ1g86NpVgNz2hcGr6BDIEZyqh9D_jr0i3N627cb3VPWtuMGKoEqKtTc7atmfMBN2Szj1-XaFlxUGPFhCVqNAuH4GY7qLFv4RBCtOLolE3iwd2PyGOICqkDC7NaM5YJcKhrzCSaooj_IRbLBz5zOeNkEc4WeuaREOqthUJobULVTiJOYreex6_BrHZ5XQcTmW_zzpGm0BkpOxW_pCgLjQZoWTMAk3lHvrpX5V-sLix-epgAdcDrvm8SVNEpb3SEJbu6s2VT8w9lZjiCngcC_jOIcZeq64J0cb3R36xA3mw1Yv2fnyXOQzgZvw3oLDl1Hm5FNYr8ugbpZvkMsMAU%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9Hi45RJ0grM/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9Hi45RJ0grM/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周一在华盛顿特区白宫椭圆形办公室举行的签字仪式上签署了行政命令。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Jim Lo Scalzo/EPA&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;海上风电受到打击&lt;/strong&gt;。特朗普下令&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=be63c1005c2c4a6890f66ef1ce035e8c&amp;amp;_e=mbZ-Iv2SEgh9k3FYOEs2zTKWM33jiaNX9P4-ERibhHQA_QPi8XqdCTreI8NzI1nUGFbU3N4Kfkbjso7lUZqN3k4CwcMi7I0NVqtgWGsIpEyRYF-WEyk0-Vuw4yp97JybInQMw2ca5HqpGbTwgIkw2eFqfSa2enxGmAaQIwEImCy008Ku-YFLwz7XF8Ex3ioLx7iaIot8gbOInOAX8lNN0x295gYdRiTyXpY7fGiYagnUp1igt-I_grrln0b1Ck0xLdAfRnI-R603r37A5Vg73A1CbNzgc0a-dgYs4idpPjstmZkbKAho-DITCaDOE0HJtvjuCHvnwAB9UHP-5aN1sSwcbsxhC3eu8d5Zji4RcJq1lw4p-CSBNFpYWWWMI-iLvNdY07HiZGHo1mh1Sm3JjvgMEbAPbjmgnpbtXKHLyhXoCs2LXq2BXxi453aDlD26nysRKQsTeyKFHc-vFlp-FocGeXlU3czrzvCnK5IE2rxuuYEWLOBWonBKwSl7FssSE5BTi4pQqbAlFTzXhim6DBsfVjGzaHVwddF3so2gpnOhh7_AoU--ufrAWWoxytk6sVmIh_f9qKRaxnkshUDdWb4kG_99gs_hpmdrcwMOMg0wgbzK66bGl0iNm2qXy1P58SMLhMI4BrMXytvcW-qt65joWZggsQLNngE4jTq-B8YTAtWYY3Ltt8HTktODzkQfWt_uQS7WGFQ2unurB7wWnkfJQydNtKfc04zy4HJfuYUTKPulSulTwW388c2hphutLDkF7YjEUHAXQLjt-ax-EgSmhfcktu_-jezVcrZQQHs%3D" target="_blank"&gt;冻结大规模可再生能源项目的许可&lt;/a&gt;。他还排除了在全国所有沿海水域出售新风电租赁的可能性，援引了前任用来阻止海上石油钻探的相同法律权力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;石油和天然气得到较大提振&lt;/strong&gt;。作为化石燃料政策&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=be63c1005c2c4a6890f66ef1ce035e8c&amp;amp;_e=mbZ-Iv2SEgh9k3FYOEs2zTKW