开发的变革。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;电动汽车支持正面临危险。&lt;/strong&gt;特朗普命令他的政府&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=be63c1005c2c4a6890f66ef1ce035e8c&amp;amp;_e=mbZ-Iv2SEgh9k3FYOEs2zTKWM33jiaNX9P4-ERibhHQA_QPi8XqdCTreI8NzI1nUmavShuOIR3WS0nehnG9DxmiSL0wPxnTlWX8mbPasd02Ggkc48o1KnuZAyy2LygFZbr01-KJ-_VsDn2vPdKqNXIzyPGOHt-RBSdktlA3sUby7TMz7711IaLpAiDAQzwAkRxM8UGAni9YT43GqlBsaDuW4j_Zqo7_CLaahMHgbTFAaMpEZ98ddKhFCs3sL4RlRFnh2ztyfCbLqxZoTx6RYTfyTmCD1L2b2_5t8pFs40ynxKD-IZVIPge-6cnI00WxxH2IiicbGNdYYjApafUyA3vFm4D1oi3XJMFxsNXpfnWD0o7svX__oSN8u6Z-bAi4FbAvMV9pgbzLp11KseVgBFhumVv-RNxJ9vBqRv8IgRMqrSaBO2xF56hSnIRfGZEaNMhtCNrg0V_aY8vc7q4rNi8aDp2juV7oNOR6sz4PKQY331WHftrQF50-8EYOklEX8Ksss8syEZhUZEcHWcPFOl9Fz95r7OOyIGGLPQy3tkUR661cCCTSSO-ysW1oOpbkyVqc-7adHFwfQM_3aYFl44JbzLeTGQMeCbHUfwBajNMahBWNr0UhTjx_VPMR1Z2Hn2LcLifkySVPh2Ebg5WGS_Ms9uUHhqyZdbzb6LApdQ-C-9HHk8M-bWQjijMFWrtHtop-UBO2pnZTKJ8lqqmrJVc1puTsRHCaoi3VXac6JaPH89J2M11fLgdw1A_L7vrTL0qYyP9zjdC4Da02YOuMqxE3eMwZPoZfa15vq8D97DPFOOkzYRSKN7QVZvUfMm8Xd" target="_blank"&gt;考虑取消补贴和其他有利于电动汽车的政策&lt;/a&gt;。该指令特别要求终止允许各州限制汽油动力汽车销售的豁免。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自达沃斯的明信片&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;作者： &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=be63c1005c2c4a6890f66ef1ce035e8c&amp;amp;_e=mbZ-Iv2SEgh9k3FYOEs2zTKWM33jiaNX9P4-ERibhHTOndBbxbydZcnAu1SeH87MU2fMml2m7CGyYLfauFfe85W46dhItnp2QOXKGwnmFGYpvllatlC5MKm0fd_VEuoYqvE8L7_-_P5rRgE1c-jiRVU5-uDj3au9lvEab7Vp-KvldQKxNb4p0Fp6HHcnaGh9Nse8ddRq6mFE3iZjMWTkWHioPmSWUpav8qoQOFZg_pWm3Jn4BUOpdBI0aTnZSH2MK7WHN6YpFLdKfCXp77zDEDeV1CUgCS1awSgzIh0WOJ-swvavFpKFf_GE4FEJNz2pJ_D9W_wPo4hzJPOkez5lqCh23bbkH0