collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;深入探讨：迁移问题&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;数百万移民&lt;/strong&gt;正面临着残酷的现实——准备被驱逐出境或被阻止进入美国。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;特朗普&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;只花了几分钟&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8aee7b3e4328403a8a7cdfcde1c3e84f&amp;amp;_e=87j0JkzkL_D4mufG8vqFW_m5ghRNlCJ4vRwkxyeenzUnXFsmso6EAb071Lw_1fzpwzLTzegyv3OBJcDLvkENM6YjGdJeYX1vhEHNiQavZRbsM1qagiNp_rcf7kpYPX1ay7dljZ4UGNZfd2YSftj5DyKuCgy4xAWyGZ_8xhzdhO5lDfgipiSCv3uW8mnZH8FQPyCtvGBoUao5YbTaTweWXsY5AOVQqdbq-75XU8N6nxEzAvjebQyq7pcOenuON03kJpg_NDCpCMhCoQyXj2p7oqwY8nZs8G0jUFHvB5yaqW5S_W1XIsCMDOYytp0bIr1HhKvJ2tjriIEIrEvsP8F30K5kC39ny1mMm8sjhZdHOqZOALVITGzDPiJI0gsEQa9McwCDe_UNqjdV9WX4J3-k41eKnoaqFxZkwnF2khQwj7qhvbvsYy-iqny1ilchvPzaGH1_N8-NwtIsuEe1uMwjaVnOsTlDrF_KJR9RCRDlSSAVIpIjV9sHAlc24f-X4f1A1vTU3_dUdgD0JC_2-fUpmj55_rXhXKG3DRq5L8xhnuhGVDnRJjlc7EWZjVV0gJdxd6jKCymtg7ZAXXBGeUSnTmFj0nEkEU4fLeOOdxs40gnZvPIBY9-bUcEpOZ-GI-avFIpb5ECDP-s4C6EDekk5RJJbuLiKY4GWwK_IJPgL0mGXu1JpxXPNwYDqXFob05Vs5FjsEvoVUs_e8baXWnBbSk9hXoYX8YjS2AS_t5GPQ6WMTYoCs--8b_7NSafvZqMOp4ut3YR_N3JOTrRVaIT1leUkJa7TDft4DRHCWLX-UsszxiaMi6TE6hx-GvnDI28o_9nyrF8Vvoc8_Wa1sqI33A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;就关闭了 CBP One&lt;/a&gt; ，这是一款许多移民用来越境寻求庇护的应用程序。他还采取行动终止与生俱来的公民权，并动员军队加强边境执法。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;纽约、芝加哥、丹佛和圣地亚哥等地的&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;移民社区&lt;/strong&gt;正准备迎接最早于周二开始的移民突击搜查。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;不过，实施这些计划&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;并不容易&lt;/strong&gt;。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8aee7b3e4328403a8a7cdfcde1c3e84f&amp;amp;_e=87j0JkzkL_D4mufG8vqFW_m5ghRNlCJ4vRwkxyeenzUnXFsmso6EAb071Lw_1fzpmuzWK_Ba8terH5AJfaSxPEEdRtm9HNROtKRCZdUVYAs2iPlLrf5ZPfYVCZP7EWzxSDnEWzMyc9I4GeBhQ_k6N21NdYB3dnt9a7G7GAwJJvqOkGqeT8dvGZaSqr_yR4uBu9hoJIQMF5W4NvAqcbIJn2oXBnr_vuEWEPtHSzNBggN9HEp03qvk3PwHEZa52eC_kj9LTDFGQefGq0X80CagP4VF8_2SB4s7xYPd0PKPN6fgaVWjjOCLo9pLWkKivMjc5CaInIOf_Q12ijmzSwNkSu1__BJb5NUh_d582qMfD8FrKCaLvEuI5tO_1hyWN9yk1iUgXGhx-Qa6ggUsBQ1ueeqxHSk_ceFa81qUVH_Zfi1mLC0-KB9pKtJKJRZRu7K7z20nUrME01xGD7giqKCwt2ylxVGK01dhTYk5V-RQvUZ59JfamR4gCNFhKg-nqn0OthlhEgwMhJP_0Xi2sn_mLBcqcOY2yqDt_JKsvxhp_kw_msivSVeIFwQzjPlDVNtOr9fu8-w5RtqAIgW5NEllPYYtrLAc7CkB3j1dRvuWWS0z3GjXcaQu7DgvFXhJojNkhIShXakt-XNun0iOmpmAVo1LQWIqT6q1ZsUvlE9BMPCq6lleA2vFETxfMNutCY3Bmh6VrLoX1DpshgVmsJUPAmOmYFbZYjwWwUNoN5vJnJOtoGldwZYw4kXBwlZcBnWeiJprv-9H2zIvEWmxcvROneNPTA8Q5JvthNtvX8JHzC99v82vp2nbFqRzX5toHIhYQWxP87zjqT_coxLL4FyzrciXr9OVtuuAMvmeXQKotLQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;移民倡导者起诉特朗普&lt;/a&gt;试图终止在美国出生的儿童的自动公民身份。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;阅读我们的解释&lt;/strong&gt;，了解特朗普的大规模驱逐计划&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8aee7b3e4328403a8a7cdfcde1c3e84f&amp;amp;_e=87j0JkzkL_D4mufG8vqFW_m5ghRNlCJ4vRwkxyeenzUnXFsmso6EAb071Lw_1fzpFM_rFyeMiSTS5m7oBYiUu2Yn1KkORgQiT1QyEWiCHK-0QDKN6o7JDh7yopvvMzIHEBp1ljMOQp2ApyjfvNW7f73cgTBReP-K3LrWq3A8iG52Nsa_p3z4mr7m8_-66tsBaZLiDZip1UHuW1g4hZg5bgQRN3kkPdYgohU4XhRdwL8D2_xNfGTrl6371Pi3skk4faH5SDfuTAxqXJgQDL9fGFhPdNmrEq7qypjJTjFspWrgBgD05OIre3KvFAwR7M0Vd8mG7Uq7_tsDarW63vv3CV9h0E5QCFvaluJzlocifoT6sVnIhYoF_SO5eULrd5DzWK_VH0AVKpusoanlU-jG-G4tFSAoeNUXdRjAdWjqjtxwz6xfvB6vMVLr5VazGgrZtMVC7Bg