ica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;火灾风险&lt;/strong&gt;。飓风强度的圣安娜风将为南加州带来每小时 100 英里的阵风，引发“特别危险”的红旗警告。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8aee7b3e4328403a8a7cdfcde1c3e84f&amp;amp;_e=87j0JkzkL_D4mufG8vqFW_m5ghRNlCJ4vRwkxyeenzUnXFsmso6EAb071Lw_1fzpwPT4LiCJ-4802HS2gl_8bzH3bhDNVIU02MMxTyTnr5x2375-x3uTscUhxZbQF9ncMbBOQ9sqKqMfKyHWnWXmPJdXn7FKXhJTZx1kakJlaxb6crRi6xvSZ8vTKe_RYCtinOoHOvvnZg1Kx00K-A1KDYCfe7ZTuAk21ufNEc--YO0ubQarZ2i_ZLO9lAnt_UMn1FzGp3v_dxZANLBQCTfgQH986pdzj6-NYq27D-S1BzSMFQ0P59qksyE4bD-dRkAkrcRcYqL67BvugxUTZO-x7gNsCSBOVrax5EZomKJxzjptZ_NTqgG6I3kVoBhne7Wz4Ry2VReUmNCHxj3HeV9205Me1soFDHJ02_0eQ6rr1-mr20TPup1cN5xxrkHfi1OPcsZf35Wij7V0n1Qly2_-WmF2wkrnByt8Ze4FkoN-txmquvfet1VW5uIEzef6S2EalvU3yk20ADeQ73mmKulv84wUkQh3kPW-LoNfWD6VsC6Dn5p9P7N23dh1fS6fnyuZLinOATehCUbj2AVBjVi91kUhnL5fZeObOPjU26fXYU32l4fUnwxbnW9G3flalyYlgGB8fB9B-Cn_RC_b_lNPHQavhFZzY7UljYL3uqMFDFhwMyEMooPmzTMfCSyvFWL5zzgmK5MmXAMXf1TX1SEghBNpgfdhb27gT1bRCYVp4Ikw6iMzqMKwk10zCHgkIMxSDMrkgEGB_82XacwqepYMmeOhbc-1abXY2ZoRJQQwfXP2FSJqHQeXEfshBFrzCHZurOScBG4FG5PTTCxh1aD5uw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;野火的威胁&lt;/a&gt;可能会持续整个星期。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8aee7b3e4328403a8a7cdfcde1c3e84f&amp;amp;_e=87j0JkzkL_D4mufG8vqFW_m5ghRNlCJ4vRwkxyeenzUnXFsmso6EAb071Lw_1fzpwPT4LiCJ-4802HS2gl_8bzH3bhDNVIU02MMxTyTnr5x2375-x3uTscUhxZbQF9ncMbBOQ9sqKqMfKyHWnWXmPJdXn7FKXhJTZx1kakJlaxb6crRi6xvSZ8vTKe_RYCtinOoHOvvnZg1Kx00K-A1KDYCfe7ZTuAk21ufNEc--YO0ubQarZ2i_ZLO9lAnt_UMn1FzGp3v_dxZANLBQCTfgQH986pdzj6-NYq27D-S1BzSMFQ0P59qksyE4bD-dRkAk14EgSuwEJv-b1Bd__k_WfYur7BH_wp_x0-kphyOjphZj1-sULeTA8fN25Y9QcA0pyhBKrNI0qAGA0ZRm19_xYV80bUj4DqBnrAG91cDWWLM6hch7OEmJ425b5QjSKm0LAZ_a07JFnPQJ1GPWzyeYW3hMxKx2kczFPRLbOQKSZs94yWVGc_tUgALH6L-R8-EoQKBduby_4f-pjyOudd_Q-8jpihj0N7WfQ8c2XbrA3Mbc2F1I-4FT0NmiH6bFX-wxFDeo7MXouYiaXQJmmiKgmU46eA93_j_upUxvGciav4-lEGgNe1tvdsAERmuU09Vp