jO01bXWSF27IPlG8zkloasfPyHNLp0PVueoUJnDegUN_ciBJV8dceAr0wnYwCSRf-G3VM8YTyXdEu5bMX_aQ7p5GH_IKBgzQPoEN1SzkDiJwljhWu3rrlk4M6SGHzdXe4Pb2JkYkLOcGVTxJNuOJcEnaGu-ApA_UApvBEFr1clsJ7SZoyXxh6qlzbI6K5TZ3NhOpDk51ndD9HgGIPN0xVmjBrIFma2xEIICN2HsXxmQUColx7zVQn16ahe_2Eg3kYbizvijXChItwdNXVV9KzSNZAyIThDlU5E8AderOaGi0LQ7SL6VvgUhDiamXw7VhsbptuyHYpGh4h1pTzYjLTnTJXZLQCMaN"&gt;退出&lt;/a&gt;世界卫生组织和巴黎气候协定的行动，而欧盟则接到指示，如果想避免关税，就应该“迅速”购买更多美国石油和天然气。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;另一方面，中国暂时逃脱了制裁。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美国盟友（尤其是欧洲盟友）面临的直接挑战是，如果对共同价值观和前景的期望被“美国优先”政策和粗鲁言辞所取代，如何处理与自由世界领导人的关系。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;欧洲夹在美国的经济民族主义和咄咄逼人的俄罗斯构成的军事威胁之间，迫切需要领导力来维护其利益。但德国即将举行的经济困境和法国的政治动荡削弱了这两个最大大国的声音。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普经常对俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京表示钦佩，普京&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=6d80d6eb015c4d9ab4847398deb7d51e&amp;amp;_e=J_V9Jcpw8zMcidWMFIs6NHHRBTNt8EcyHCJfD5iARK1x_uo3o7nJyG6WZ2I-U2U2mbKA5NsCaz3Ai9XXmmatZhEebh3iT_cQyNNa-VLSZB_tIDiczXZ-N_qDK7yE397nSgb5S-DXsSSi99-DBrMmOfJB_2xKgPQXZg8Jz1axPnU_oNdBDYRzhtNvw9naDvGi8ehF0CNmBMevx-CtzKT6vdERKCKqZ8OhW61H5hQP1tNGmMtfd0ZV99NBdDILi7uAgeUeu_sofkCtt8FavFG7IKCA93l1gQ8o-yORrAC0-p_NqZa4k8LgYBYi3wV_96S16dxJPZMAEKuMKYTh4Zo9kxOBJAGLgSECXGDSKhPeleq2FSb8YD63vODrCwv2aLdHXah6dYAu-ZTX0j5vXPlVqmzMJxYFC-ZTzqH7i497GXO8lm_Ic4PgDgVhuqaV-pr-z1F_ToqcNOP-vASSulVUBTNqP8h_ilpJpE4MQXidR5gd9QB1dua2ANEQuvQxiNGAA2qM6NiPeurgOJSJwn0ky-H4Pk_Ak6bRGYV8Z93u2yvKDfbNhiTBsRRjG6Ax6ZCm4o_3ezjICGujgSeI7iUysm99miDpIxHiqa4n0mQHXnPWe_-jkOtJyQmoq32fUrnkLO7qwP9KnJVWkArNrPK-cSwJpgEW6xUsrIT3VIK1bcZKfckwQoaO1IwVMmqnKjdalwytbSRL3bdfik-uNtwIUJ__V5FNaVX0zuG2aH5ZPtIJSNp0vfmo9sJgxrO40-Zw9vwKVvxT5d0zptUpmClcX0ISdmU_muzPIsIeCQ5saqBfD9kWyvoFTP8qJ1F5A6gz"&gt;渴望就结束乌克兰战争的协议进行谈判&lt;/a&gt;。欧洲领导人面临着由他们自己决定欧洲大陆未来安全的风险。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;像加拿大和墨西哥一样，他们现在必须面对一位毫不犹豫地对长期盟友行使权力、而且其利益可能不再与他们一致的美国总统。 &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;— &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=6d80d6eb015c4d9ab4847398deb7d51e&amp;amp;_e=J_V9Jcpw8zMcidWMFIs6NHHRBTNt8EcyHCJfD5iARK3-uD_6ZlwAQVulKJBys1t7hwo0TE4ftfR_B7-pHgoiGORcUlXnrliYDDJf9-ScB622qfjzRXKM3NCOUz-U6x7nfhlbYy68dyF_IiJXxjflO_uXKY3p7yIsN4lY_lTHRYGmtGM6uCQsGEWshvSfJqUh7twthO7Ali1Ddi-IXgopOS3ggDqgXgJWJDBosTZLKcmOqIXAW61Nk6AnS8jHoWEPfYvUirER13b8xRN2KNAVC1E1YUDIq330HOhHnY3bAr4I75-8NbsfH5C7Pb-NGWmk5O28COt-l_NPWZcRX2qnOrUl178Zz_UKp0DwofzHdq7WIF-mGfDDr6HK7eXSoKu-3HYEjbfiXt1hhGTF9PF5MLXYK6oU0wBaGZ_qJn3hjFw%3D" target="_blank"&gt;托尼·哈尔平&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=6d80d6eb015c4d9ab4847398deb7d51e&amp;amp;_e=J_V9Jcpw8zMcidWMFIs6NHHRBTNt8EcyHCJfD5iARK0ySXtm5MJBmNC1XkyNDcnrMaDYSRkQOzS5RywXzHU9DYVsYSav4tOBNoFSUGupPfI8q4AgAqJ3OF1U9f_8KSJW1Blfn4Gjll98WDL_qoSCT_yTolXb3oJuoei7LMdp1w9EFUIHBXPn7ptpdUNLjB7b6DZiNhx9lNO_4ymmlV0B2Pm9W-YPgqF18UrFgzIcSO9FtTDCrkG_gs96-SyFT9Y00phYS9pcJSzv56UeBlP-zCZt6Je9Qqm1LLgkk7wRaXCnvITSqrIYGqDQqn0ShIZG9dh_D29935xg_tYF81j4Rv83F6iU1mfc4YIML_NJB2mCU7HHYtIoJvnrpPyFkBN0VxxfdY3W_w0osF-iEdVEqsOBIDrgt-mVqMSbJ7ocb-YbjvTtWl_nXuwrFQgXLW1Ix6AaT6JJGizREflQO9VE0Ad-n0nLTgxwsKBnE2y77OI5LdN3jGLvPcv47IdCt7But2-YjpAbpf3WwQWi-0rOIhbv2uizc2GxvH9cplx44oCU2u8jEjrWazCYG0OPQyA9Ox2ZePongfyhEbaBnQnjtoQFEoOGBFldNY39FVy5qOZaUzDRfzUvZHjj97PI_b9Y_LtLG4Mu-68jcJyq7bAqtF8x-xCpHvy8y8E6-HLK6LIe-fp2nlGmDnPasf9YBs7jwaKdqbVlK9XuEVE_4GcfMP00xfHcevs2Ydf5lc2f3ppRtHbmbJb8aTAo_tsN3y3Hu7IsBTwg2E_B2dNrjvG37Q%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0dRm.j9Le3k/v0/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:no