UNDsvGrwprmjZ0w9RD0SM8yWNl8WaiF3kWF6OWwgKCfzgQEAkvuFnSHs7oACf0BwUnKOe8b73SnJjYdtZrH0fvq1d7CruxUGtx1ChVq5b5OP-dY%3D" target="_blank"&gt;黄金时代&lt;/a&gt;”，同时对抗“激进和腐败的建制派”。他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1osGI8Q0v2T-6skw6W57Ji-LJsuyUDxFsdDx0uLiQl7N6QTdJoGEzjN0TyK83P9jw6MABlTPlO86o-Xf1a3mngO1vS6mMLHNF4U4pU8UE_eKOtCm2okCwB8iW3_Lbx4gf4fdWac98gAr-NVNK3wZIJahmkKaclOyT0tjutZCQ5mvpM5X_IDdul_p2RH9IJqbQlIpwpohpPGuWiFDNMOqxapj5Oo75eCaAyNxmPhjLErckhMHaeFGSVs-gEKN_9-JeDqUpoNJSUzIp6uU7WCw9oRS0aMRxiM0vsGmalJiAvCCNqoJHjERUz5Y8m6-eZwCKYOc1atekuAzFklTy_fUCDADEe9CdcqaWmC3b0QvtiSOlv5zgpavbVVRr-J6DJ8CB4dgL36L3Cz3-UKOYZgwMgxBLgkZ1UjaBJU0tfDLkYNcpLNB6LvM2GnEPrlHSv9VlnWIV_rvtm9Akh5U-sMQX2jrjv2xIrTj_w9HyGMeNC5WIgyKfpg-CTqZSsR497m70RUa-UL-zB6n6iUN0rfPCFaqTlFXtjFyS4DjncCQI70Wj2q5RtMhJmENYApM68ZB4z21xmRGhuF5gJCmiwk7Ufmjs4kfsF5Fyg_CypFECV_JfIkCjSDzq9U_wdJcAHDImPXssdomFXmOF1ERbKZ47oCCsp6DGOOgsEJonBgGPKH8Xnq8XV0lPhFWYPIEWOLyWqQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;承诺通过宣布“国家能源紧急状态”来解决残余通胀&lt;/a&gt;，以鼓励更多的国内化石燃料生产，同时政策变化将允许在联邦土地上开发新的石油和天然气，并取消拜登时代的气候法规。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;尽管如此，特朗普的大部分议程仍取决于国会，共和党在参众两院均拥有微弱多数，而且在可能扩大该国巨额国债的计划上已经出现分歧。特朗普还将权衡他希望在多大程度上围绕个人不满来调整他的政府，包括他经常对自己在 2020 年选举中落败的谎言以及在离任后起诉他的努力。周一早些时候，现任前总统乔·拜登宣布赦免特朗普曾威胁要追捕的家庭成员和一些政府官员。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; 78岁的特朗普是宣誓就职的最年长的总统，也是第一位被定罪的重罪犯的总司令，也是众议院因&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1om2qs3_65ldADiUsbL6xor9pgyKgOrPsMwC7jcTWcyKOUrfc_ffogg_wNN3COL5R46JTfHzDZ4ia8osTGCgYv-Tbp5lmWtnd0M7ibbW_m6HEvzXIqnCKQBjAg5-SN7wUFm6qrR9Wf2b3al4Dgl77tpR03wTylAY9iwezoepxoJ_WeETKNGFrUetmoMwkTfp_hhDh8ivbFHc6e5qeQnRQ0Gv87IgzzX7cbAWw4nynh0n0LWaqnNV8hIIp2cQzr0qCOYhzujrj7o1lq4cv6_zZ1jjXdWOoXoroq1pyo1LtrplI8fZMlh9c7BugvqCeADKrJgjA-CYa7IBNeQTtdzVwferkTfo-BqFbTrr9Apg2741lmYcuBYd6mppol7AR4178-tD3nZZ-51vrRNaIiIBUAyhK435aqQsvW-Vr493jPCSs25lJxduhSEi2-XiLhLG4kUmPKhwEkVGxB0tpbok2liL_HoWW0bwYxQtBVQQ2J-2RjE9nY4za-MXUYiIbh5jl57eSEObSR0VB_NZP99H3Hs053bFdgNr0x62yat3-vwlggchG_jf3sumwrol1_dKfUSFMKFY-jaVw5ZAFstqWLcyedPBawm3T8U3GlnRk7n-4C-VZfhqA7y016R-pNmyrEbCpg5V1sTFY0BQDqrfbZR8%3D" target="_blank"&gt;重罪和轻罪&lt;/a&gt;两次单独弹劾的对象。尽管如此，他重返办公室&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1osGI8Q0v2T-6skw6W57Ji-ImSWk5kVtlm1GiCkeTTUkXcvcf0wLnnsi94Cgk2td__uyinTK1l6w8NP1x0l6HqyOft1r4rSw-I2SHjfUmeL3bbBTc3m_oHLiQKu2IQHZveVE5joapu-lgH9w9sQ0kKX7o_uq_MLvXCRENXHpCDkXx5r3ctw18HC3oRvQbQadOvOTyc09mCsBjMvNL3WQR3-PMJKfs1VizeiRgQ03jqxl7HJ80lce4VS3tOeGyPSxqw2AG0JAF0uK5Ssb1SlQWvw0VM93SvA7BNkas9k3KKWPFIG2neypLA77PcVTFdLt3ge2V7hBOFTt_LvGOqUBo0ffnIcctm4ltrB8X8PGq083sCG3Bg6tWrK_Ob4a__gk-Q5igxWUQXakUNKpSdfqPKoO-02sw2kgWSfwPdxZ23EKsBIKd9NX-em_RESi4tRrUq87b7GcpiKx5HiPjNRzkkbPnk5vrea8MYT0q5uULDbA89eJJbiRaKVwph-b6zOEiEZ8H4-HyHtogpiVuBPzYh0iB8-oJMOfpaEa6lFdoY0EkM4kB11jfFC_dyYT_aRbq-HTrqgLAhDbj-CqgSIPlVsQ2RTHlqeU2AFKesVMyr1NhEIcjJ2vZZY6xIW5oPZKHdZOiHksir3kMGAulun5ZQGTA-J9sqLgCN1X86LuYk5VevlBMu61JWURxMFvLjMIIcw3knsXcEL9qEiU9EJZhZCHdsFcbM0Z6UORVkOUy0T_m" target="_blank"&gt;时比以往任何时候都更加大胆&lt;/a&gt;，而且鉴于共和党完全控制了美国政府，他可能受到的检查也更少了。 &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;— &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1osGI8Q0v2T-6skw6W57Ji-I_lHdozhuFYwL6T9Yn2l1N_lo9VKCUeRlEF8RFVZp9XIE-d29NrAIJ0JJLQL2VmeJ6A0TvE6adBJLqu12_zLPFrF7czSk6WXqVnCT6P1petQ5AQyyJLhSPTW21oFJF_MVHfEIObByjFWCYlcSkKIthX-s0qcCDm8-yekC2vNcUMzWXcFrY9IGSpJA_66IsevEqqPdZKKnWO-LirUZPTdbn9C2Cy3xuWcqoClFvCr7LbCHTT-jqQqpZjVpYf8SNjEF4IrV-a3KFeLqgvrxszMuoYvxDexdy5sPf2UE68Jdkp1jQaXUTq-87s39NQG_AvJPMrMj_k3QW7ZDUqJ9wQeFM9hgAlDPVG3-8TVVDICFUuW3wuA7RKBJCLjCa_IO8ydmzT2bYUXIiXpa0S9_2dhkZ_lexsrHzpqPF5JIO7-5Q2A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;大卫·E·罗维拉&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普推迟了七年前对中国发动贸易战的承诺&lt;/strong&gt;。相反，他命令他的政府解决全球不公平贸易行为，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1osGI8Q0v2T-6skw6W57Ji-I0-d2b54SkXsSS2WADBgh364z2gsgKK76BgohW1syfItDdY5_JkFMq_zzvm-iZeChYC26ThdQqczOXV_hDBqYIcjqJ2hDoOsRopLvqiW_ExT1H5aqtvrFcBGkgJ6lpCHy78gyyQkc1ZdOheswzNIK6kPOeyaKS4_A1gznLBNtqCdrc-WP5tKiob0CYZBOxoLASUyL6aNzBLDe6NIEE1VcYmGkZ9xeDBT1TA3eXM1-4kOeDgPZrHnDVm37OygCISFieN8N0J8ak8ICsBKTso--8-b86y4RlwziuDhZxheA8Vbye7tZitptlHuskAut6FrqAfYGMO6R4zkJRFxqD_QF6Ms8ISPT-jSAZ3pW71H66XaG7S7tFEMGNUUU4Myr6ia5TK5aErRxu9Kz2d9j2W3mUiZsJleEhPUBcB-BxnJ4VMakU5KixlBWJRvqbRGD4bVornj4Nnvq08EG8CulBjp1UagS3llJDFbNyLZCWGEllJF7K_KFJNy35MBjhiMAyHKqtCZdNOe-cqfIZhRt5alzn4XP6ofoGePXAW40r2J2jru7gISrzuBenZfA3iPH06nZzbP79BaTZxnozuHR9YPjLZizWoz2JelYRg8fmocoRfdDb6et4EQNv7tyDUVLUornoQiJUsDkMCiq_HkiI1CrOOUzEOEen8MswV4azeaL8_tkbUxMk3eEV4IReer8TWTcOxbBwD8vnrcFrbi8vBBkNWo3wcPWOIEWJpvQgnqIM0o4DzZGWQkFyracOHgx_MGA%3D" target="_blank"&gt;调查北京是否遵守了&lt;/a&gt;他第一个任期内签署的协议。特朗普的第一届政府与北京谈判达成了“第一阶段”贸易协议，结束了多年来针锋相对的关税，但中国承诺购买美国商品的几乎没有兑现。特朗普今天的举动呼吁主要联邦机构解决其他国家涉嫌的货币操纵问题。在竞选季节之后，政府决定不立即针对北京，承诺对所有进口商品征收 10% 至 20% 的关税，对中国产品征收 60% 的关税。他还誓言&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1osGI8Q0v2T-6skw6W57Ji-I0-d2b54SkXsSS2WADBgh37P2tFrVZ7gcwWx6m7EkmvqqZJdDxGyXbmzYcqEW5aYfovw5PMU14GVxTpeZhrBTbVoKRIOe8U9qlkMwhzQJzWxpIuJIOWS9N08ibxOBEZt6dQTe4lQB9DmcINmX1VPOP-QMP0iCfJ2aJ8urozMn4KKrwE2fBxjptDblsKWKCn9ICxI5ZMlxUqVSkeSVVWZp2CfeRiMV4Vod8kUIncWVKnN6jZ7qKbhTfs_rWG1JgR9j3p_aYYZovu-1Hu5d7tHDbcEveGZd2WlV5TDFiMXocfAJioGz3E2Ddp6J-F-5xtOePlABxEmj6rlDH-6nLoqnt79HL_FjTjpKiMDbzPwxgekMXooGjVsP-rZ94WjFDstQ9YoAF8-xVLvVOQ_x2lBcVm56O22D8TryrLYFtYWzswpbAOZUeVWlV4FI0wbUwPZrrEskDfe0pAaNyZ3ZHBIXFfi9_3IhHXQvil-wLOD-0SqVmccnj3UsbJmSIqtsA2eUAOsETRTDLPUQ8HnC3DTl4-V6ipt-QYRV0131nTxPyitBR-1bd4Tw-unqIYki27MC0h6KNw_-joCou82MfUdHTf2VoAPu9_WT7IXJ_J4dKkJ04uWs6b1ry2XXK01KT9UfHpRJ0OGTIKo5STL_T-Co2Gy2xNpeHJO399pK6rT14bgsS7oH_M0ifLlKLeQ8Y-VmcoyIrnLDloVTcTNMQaJacFeQXlplifrCqhPZv0qwVCASqW3NdGGylPRPywq5HIcs%3D" target="_blank"&gt;对加拿大和墨西哥的所有产品征收 25% 的关税&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普承诺在移民、能源、军事和联邦劳动力等各个方面发布行政命令&lt;/strong&gt;，这使许多人试图扭转其前任的政策。他曾表示，他可能签署约 100 项行政命令，白宫周一&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1ouQFtKGDbEhzDh4xJfS5u