xcV8RQXU0HU4HClmNX0qoieDV8OFHRTxYPijYFDJ4KRZf8SjqpAk9KrmEKceAMuD_Hm6PgtdAcBbc2ER0a0Mf8yHQBpljSm3gFhFK1wjFYGsbCkgroyUu158iReVFHrs7_FUydVQwTOplH9rcoRmhZfbSsoLn7gjhpSNJ9bGOUsFLy0iBXlSY-3CASfudXVD-gNNR-LE7zdAikwNzlol0dG9nsGxa_u1khRgbwdPWVKSJe_EsRDRME5dOyZDdIUrN8Ue1DRe3O83Rb9HNMXeEZA8PZWlRqL5YycatWCu4tVQ61FrbCrMonrD75NfPtVdaQUw2a7rYt0mehaH5bsm-sKTc8YzGQUnuqACWoCWrO3lqQogR5N2s2PkPXR2P8%3D" target="_blank"&gt;该举措违反了 1972 年美国法律，该法律&lt;/a&gt;要求对与白宫有直接关系的团体进行利益冲突、意识形态平衡和透明度检查。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;一些州&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;没有等待&lt;/strong&gt;特朗普是否兑现其对国家“战略”比特币库存的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1osGI8Q0v2T-6skw6W57Ji-JXATQPoVLIO7zObOb5fiSHZWAtH0f_wgOE0zLkbx7fImOZo7ulDv9nD2-Z8Fzuhth-__IlPbT2Zxzsar3xG6N9sJMkAPNBDKi5B-BOq3GvSb2a1p6f2CQ7rDlN2vsq1sMJwC-iLXPWvJHYCro5phd52cPyVtmQyMJTWfNOQfj9ZTR0eiYOMDKbX5_4Qeqm_LZdCVQNYHnzIkLW7PvN5BxKZVjek8gyXE6uy6hQm_NP8tkqu124jyMQslCJzoNIdj2_Mgzdli0a0BwXtAxxTJyjXPaJY43YvKi2R7DzqFd9NgD2k2y16PWC2BbmGv_72xp7IEUXOywdfrakeFpyfjQ1z6SSFESvsOUh-4JTmV6NSy9LdlcJkak9kPcLsUXE9VI-mvLhgrz-nniENNKcF-9YEqwgDaAkQ0TMWxahxyT_O7yJkWMkTu_WOjdNTaoPlv7z56Ny20kSXmU3OHkFHdfhF5yUa4Ll48gunTFZFo-eKLx0XoICZfe-pK89g-q3oKqNuA4vpZb1UfkMCMB4f4ic3wQK9M8P_TQRerActmbNrCvumJPu3I-QL6q7KLvc38iUgokp3MNo6edsgh1GAzHwa_HlOCQtbF4l0IrQkC2He9JngzHo4lA4Csdw4XA85Zqy7b0wekBSEsS5i2qzHXhZZhW12ezF65TfU1A-OcGOZ9YFRama7KIus7uUq5nqOSenWjr0uTROcljRJ8af478v9jwVabX9tmzBpBviC0_rbA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;支持&lt;/a&gt;，而是将事情掌握在自己手中。随着地方立法会议的开始，八个州已经提出了提议加密货币储备的法案。但是，尽管确保州政府以某种形式持有比特币的努力在长期的加密货币倡导者中产生了动力，但这种呼声可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1osGI8Q0v2T-6skw6W57Ji-I0-d2b54SkXsSS2WADBgh39Rryw2eaf1jLvQXlo7svHBgEZ9Hvi1BJOaZULqdE3e0Bj4ClWQliAWbPVGgmVF4O88sOVegH2mCxgDHgVYRapVf8lfnHvF0qaAm_PjL8h9rw_UjMy4Lvd8kOJufnWzAegdS8_2aHMs7G5QpEP-PrrMFWN-lrJbURfT2V_0V58XFlyphEgnS2bRRBneBjDgh_HT1_r5NoN7GBGYSCVYt51Zl_xgzU3vCfjBfatX2slF34Jjtz9hsZw-wAJmovUqN3px79ZZwxGBDvp2TFjHwQCamJcWZ615d0AytrQfset8OHFVLkGou79BUIucDYyIGkVbNNDZYW8N0-uAX4RycdQ1vve9OaZ2am8bQIJ68IBRT9bfKf0NwlJxiz526CLP3jUK-oisumV0Zwebgd_7OdxMIcqruCBbUpI2phPVGkA8BGtCqSNwB-Y57SLirBFjHvsB8XJA6Oxx_7QGusYfxsnvn5hT8PQI--7fb9mmaRxzUpD8NAn5nImBEPx4E7X1Y5-eD-CXUjKpF3snoPlPJKAMM3RWe8rTLqkGbH3WygwKEwug8uYk_RxVLFKiotsL2FLzv7lEFejJGqr1aaYcaOepwlzNOLTalxz2uPx83UjBdDTKLpXagPm0jN1CVJ6lXeBXJ3C7wEi6F0bsSQLf6KW36cJ0axEnM9Im2sJWP-baF91QKI_1vMoOeu16WT2vJIWgLw36FAFUCLl9pLZDz7o1XNjPpG5gc_i4uguHOxpFg%3D" target="_blank"&gt;不仅仅是噪音&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;一些世界上最富有的人&lt;/strong&gt;周一出席活动，向特朗​​普致敬。这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1