VcJG_AgCrmuJzxB5g54lJoGnO3-fxhbHsJSDaRbBCRUwHNfTBT0SayE4B__8Ss5yEaFXQTarnqT15jJo4n5gMjoKspJwRhhISjgpE0JLCUQhXXR7Zj2ikpvC1eJTNL0CKuXdwpCn55Ilb6DSOfC7N60hOn9xM5YrUdrQBNUfDWalljeM4bhon62yFoAMqMboeTuuRlAUPCioW0qXViy2t1CEVOGt-7ARLnaSmF5HtefFIcsnN_WiNvRseFhyP5twg_JyQ0Amksm1qVa2F6bB4OgddnrPaAahX8DzEYrXGPi7mC2XT_dQe8Urc6Ie2PFFsV9vujs0wt07tMBiY_xliKuUCSK1ZkVgD8tr5N56EFPxM86dIisJ2U9nRII0kh1hy8o7a8i_9fEIMwk8Kbi-fU4v0IDRO7CH35izMIQAPkM5LacNgcmYdkeE0Fg0Co0kQmrgilP-1OXsHJoTwqkR85-1XhlikAPvmg1MQuhBoAkjsIQacNDsyqf8kftYFVprnr8WVGtxcT69ZuTo00ZxwZFRJg4kbSUBeUgSed7iCzzrHtV_oaFPwmINoCZdqk4riAEOkQsliWcvkXU7eKUouSRPGJvMOwxTEF5pXa1OzLOaFBSdeKns6OQsUDeNAGVc7wZePZUOH7qcefW5pGkmMu2-OiD1jnQc8MHmusUDqCJbTshdOMx0B0jQVm896IxkouTkXU%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOlY7vvmbFvY/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOlY7vvmbFvY/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;从左至右，马克·扎克伯格、杰夫·贝佐斯、桑达尔·皮查伊和埃隆·马斯克在唐纳德·特朗普在美国国会大厦圆形大厅举行的就职典礼上。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Julia Demaree Nikhinson/美联社照片&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e5ff9f21edcd4884b076c1f4f03f35b6&amp;amp;_e=hqA-ibQj5TXk5i_IYBV1ojemnyhEBg1aNxuABa2AHBlezcBH6Q3Qf2qeGIc0aSKo3ttBEmVQMh7ip4gD4wzqF0V-8Su6a7utRKSGR4ZQrSO3AgcAVbhOtsZGXTB_7TpIhKEdF89_YDvvRXuA